{"tid":1167570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新聞街拍播一半！緊T妹「震盪超兇長輩」甜笑路過　形狀激美...網全歪樓","createTime":"2019-05-23T06:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T03:30:06.000Z","uid":32511,"like":236,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"83274ca622af75d11700822cef2e4f9f594689a0","tid":1167570,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"日本《TOKYO MX NEWS》新聞台日前在播報一起「炸彈預告」報導，背景是新宿區一般街頭，畫面突然拍到一個路人從店裡走出，她的火辣身材瞬間吸走觀眾注意力，在網路上引起熱烈討論，害網友全都歪樓。<br />\n<br />\n日本新聞台日前播報一則炸彈客攻擊預告，嫌犯激動表示要把自己工作的地方全都炸掉，當時新聞畫面拍到新宿區街頭的某條商店街，其中一間店裡突然走出一個長髮正妹，臉上掛滿甜美笑容，再往下一看，因為穿著緊身上衣，上圍的飽滿形狀看得一清二楚，超兇畫面搶走觀眾注意力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4113/d4113333.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4113%2Fd4113333.jpg&h=e7cff0a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然只有拍到一瞬間的畫面，但有網友眼明手快截圖，迅速在網路上流傳，引起一陣熱烈討論，「果然民間還是有很多正妹」、「素人顏值也太高了吧」、「這身材太完美了，至少有G吧」、「有點肉肉的最好」、「結果大家全忘了這則新聞在報什麼」、「這樓歪慘了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQEYX9h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQEYX9h.jpg&h=4688a8ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n界波袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0590b074d15eb0fc1b507d9805c199fb32e4d8bf","tid":1167570,"uid":103645,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09056da17d6bdb572668697fea9cea0aac3a2330","tid":1167570,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T06:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=